properties.media:imagetext:
Food and drinks are served right after takeoff, but if you'd like to be
served later, no problem. Just ask your in-flight team.
BREAKFAST
ENTRÉES
Breakfast is served with a flaky buttery croissant.
Contains wheat, dairy, and sugar
POACHED EGG & BRISKET BREAKFAST PATTY
Hot breakfast patty of smoked beef brisket, roasted
fingerling potatoes, peppers, and onions. Roasted root
vegetables, poached cage free egg, horseradish creme
fraiche, and chervil.
Contains beef, egg, and dairy
SAVORY PUMPKIN PANCAKES & SCRAMBLED EGGS
Fluffy pumpkin spice pancakes, cage free scrambled
eggs, blistered cherry tomato, honey roasted pear and
persimmons. Served with real maple syrup.
Contains dairy, wheat, sugar, and egg
Hot entrées are served with a fruit salad of fresh
grapefruit, orange, mango, kiwi, and blueberries.
HEARTY CANNELLINI BEAN SOUP WITH WILD
MUSHROOMS
Pureed white bean soup deliciously seasoned with
onions, garlic, leks, and herbs. Topped with sautéed
wild mushrooms, pine nuts, and herbed feta cheese.
Contains optional dairy and pine nuts
DESSERT
PECAN PIE
contains nuts, dalry, wheat, sugar, and egg
SNACKS ANYTIME
TOP SHELF BITES
Nibble on a spread of delectable Dean & Deluca snacks
throughout the flight.
Rest assured, your second choice will be just as delicious.
LUNCH & DINNER
Flights Departing after 10am
APPETIZER
Flights over four hours
ROASTED KABOCHA & MIXED GREENS SALAD
Dandelion greens and radicchio, five-spice roasted
kabocha squash, and dried dates. Garnished with
shaved parmesan cheese and a pomegranate
vinaigrette.
Contains optional dairy
Flights four hours and under
SIMPLE SALAD
Mesclun mix with chives, chervil, basil leaves, and
cherry tomatoes. Served with an olive oil-balsamic
vinaigrette.
Lunch and Dinner are served with a Multigrain Roll
contains wheat
ENTRÉES
DIJON CHICKEN
Boneless skinless chicken thigh, roasted with dijon
mustard, vermouth, and herbs. Roasted potatoes,
sautéed leeks and onions, wild mushrooms, kale, and a
sherry mustard jus. Topped with chopped pistachios
and parsley bread crumbs.
Contains poultry, dairy, sugar, optional nuts and wheat
